author: sky.cactus
content: This question doesn't really make sense.  If you want to spin up a private network, download one or more of the clients and configure it to run a private network.

author: sky.cactus
content: Any of the execution clients will support this.  Take your pick which one to use, and follow the instructions for that tool on configuring and starting a private network

author: meowbroski

author: jgm
content: No, that is about the method used by the layer 1 to come to consensus.  A layer 2 network will be separate, sending its proofs to layer 1 for security.  To find out about layer 2 testnets you should visit their own Discords.  You can find details about various layer 2 solutions at https://l2beat.com/
